After the ith patient being included, the set of acceptable doses (in terms of DLT), that excludes overly toxic doses, is estimated as follows:
(9)𝒜i={dj∈𝒟:dj≤argmindj∈𝒟|F^1j(t∗,λ1j,λ2j)−πDLT|}
with F^1j(t∗,λ1j,λ2j), the vector of estimates of choice for F1j(t,λ1j,λ2j) at each dose level, given available data.
